org.jimmutable.core.serialization.writer

Interface StandardWritable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Book, BookDeckList, BookDeckMap, BookDeckSet, BrandCode, EmailAddress, FieldName, ItemAttribute, ItemKey, ItemSpecifications, NullPrimative, ObjectID, PartNumber, PhoneNumber, PhoneNumberDeck, PhoneNumberDigits, StandardImmutableDeck, StandardImmutableListDeck, StandardImmutableMapDeck, StandardImmutableObject, StandardImmutableSetDeck, StandardObject, Stringable, TimezoneID, TypeName

    public interface StandardWritable
    An interface that must be implemented by all (non-primitive) objects that wish to be writable by ObjectWriter. Notably, StandardObject implements StandardWritable (meaning that ObjectWriter can write any StandardObject)
    Author:
    jim.kane
